g">Lãm Bá trung thừa kiêm tử điệt số nhân trừ quan chế từ, nhân thuật phụ tử huynh đệ tứ mỹ tải ca ty luân - 覽柏中丞兼子侄數人除官制詞因述父子兄弟四美載歌絲綸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/Ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-gi%C3%A1-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-kinh-chu-tr%C3%BA-%C6%B0-Thu%C3%BD-%C3%81i-ch%C3%A2u/poem-ecBB2WEk8qg0uvbtKAu4Bg">Ngự chế đại giá thượng kinh chu trú ư Thuý Ái châu - 御制大駕上京舟駐於翠靄洲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ph%C3%BA/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Tr%C3%BA-Thu%C3%BD-%C3%81i-ch%C3%A2u/poem-ZVkZllpYGoIDXXstEdAPkg">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Trú Thuý Ái châu” - 奉和御製駐翠靄洲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ph%C3%BA/author-6psImpn4SbleLfrcnYcyQA">Phạm Đạo Phú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%A7n-trung-ng%C3%A2m-k%E1%BB%B3-01-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-h%C3%B4n/poem-AVPDg1j6aHacww5HrXCEDw">Tần trung ngâm kỳ 01 - Nghị hôn - 秦中吟其一－議婚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%ABa-v%C4%83n-H%C3%A0-B%E1%BA%AFc-ch%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-nh%E1%BA%ADp-tri%E1%BB%81u-hoan-h%E1%BB%89-kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-02/poem-2-E6i7XL9v6_M5wxfWID6w">Thừa văn Hà Bắc chư đạo tiết độ nhập triều, hoan hỉ khẩu hào tuyệt cú kỳ 02 - 承聞河北諸道節度入朝歡喜口號絕句其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
